00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:03.140
to have you here, Mister Kihara.

00:06:03.140 --> 00:06:05.130
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:06:05.130 --> 00:06:09.410
&gt;&gt; Maureen Cohen Harrington:
So, for anime questions, I'm --

