Unlike Anthony, I
am new to anime.

00:06:12.610 --> 00:06:14.420
So where do you start?

00:06:14.420 --> 00:06:17.070
What -- As I am just
learning for the first time,

00:06:17.070 --> 00:06:19.620
what in your words, in
other people's words,

00:06:19.620 --> 00:06:22.850
do you think is a good
thing to see or to study

00:06:22.850 --> 00:06:27.510
or to enter this world?

00:06:27.510 --> 00:06:45.900
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:06:45.900 --> 00:06:48.890
&gt;&gt; Speaker 2: I think it's true
for everybody that you want

00:06:48.890 --> 00:06:53.510
to see something that's
made in your own country.

00:06:53.510 --> 00:07:19.920
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:23.480
I think that you
should see what people

00:07:23.480 --> 00:07:25.370
in your country have made.

00:07:25.370 --> 00:07:27.840
Walt Disney's, you know,
"Steamboat Willie," [inaudible]

00:07:27.840 --> 00:07:32.280
