not by children, of course.

00:07:42.510 --> 00:07:45.050
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:07:45.050 --> 00:07:49.510
Grown ups made something
for the children.

00:07:49.510 --> 00:07:58.040
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:07:58.040 --> 00:08:02.700
So I think it's the best to
see something that was made

00:08:02.700 --> 00:08:07.510
for children in your
own country.

00:08:07.510 --> 00:08:10.050
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:08:10.050 --> 00:08:13.840
If you think that's
amazing, the next step is

00:08:13.840 --> 00:08:16.010
to see something
from other countries.

00:08:16.010 --> 00:08:17.310
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:08:17.310 --> 00:08:21.550
Definitely it is I grew
up on Disney cartoons.

00:08:21.550 --> 00:08:22.850
&gt;&gt; Maureen Cohen
Harrington: Really?

00:08:22.850 --> 00:08:26.850
&gt;&gt; Speaker 2: I loved
the [inaudible] brothers.

00:08:26.850 --> 00:08:32.860
I think it's the same
as everybody, right?

00:08:32.860 --> 00:08:34.610
&gt;&gt; Maureen Cohen Harrington: So
what about your work, though?

00:08:34.610 --> 00:08:36.770
When we're ready to move
to your work or if we want

00:08:36.770 --> 00:08:38.360
to just skip a step
