00:14:58.510 --> 00:15:02.020
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:15:02.020 --> 00:15:04.310
When I was in high school
I took a studio tour,

00:15:04.310 --> 00:15:07.010
and I wanted to --

00:15:07.010 --> 00:15:08.310
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:15:08.310 --> 00:15:15.510
But then Hayo Miyazaki liked
me, and then we made "Nausicaa."

00:15:15.510 --> 00:15:18.070
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:15:18.070 --> 00:15:22.010
Then I graduated college, and
then officially joined Topcraft.

00:15:22.010 --> 00:15:23.440
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:15:23.440 --> 00:15:28.510
