movie called "Nausicaa."

00:15:43.480 --> 00:15:46.510
So please, you know,
work on that.

00:15:46.510 --> 00:15:50.040
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:15:50.040 --> 00:15:53.390
[Inaudible] is the --
[Inaudible] is the person,

00:15:53.390 --> 00:15:59.010
the president, of
Ghibli at the time.

00:15:59.010 --> 00:16:00.310
[ Foreign Language Spoken ]

00:16:00.310 --> 00:16:06.510
