&gt;&gt; Anthony Dunn: Did you work
on the animation of "Code Geass"

00:35:52.930 --> 00:35:54.520
or just the entire story?

00:35:54.520 --> 00:35:56.750
&gt;&gt; Speaker 2: He's just
introducing the people

00:35:56.750 --> 00:35:59.900
who worked on it for working
at Ghibli at the time,

00:35:59.900 --> 00:36:05.380
who were working on these
other different works.

00:36:05.380 --> 00:36:08.060
He can answer that.

00:36:08.060 --> 00:36:09.360
Personally [inaudible].

